metadata.name: VAN GOGH STYLE by GIORGIONE  "To the Next Earth"
metadata.description:
This oil painting on 30 x 40 cm canvas is a tribute to the famous post-impressionist painter Vincent van Gogh, in his own style. "One of the most famous figures in the history of Western art"

The painting has been varnished and I will be sent framed.  

WORLDWIDE SHIPPING

A digitally rendered, stylized pixel-art version of my painting in the NextEarth metaverse on a precious plot of land near The Hague (Netherlands). The fancy name of my work is: "To the NextEarth", referring to that the most popular web3 map-based metaverse is on its way to the moon! :)
The painting in three parts is currently not for sale on the marketplace. It will later be possible to merge the three pieces.  

https://app.nextearth.io/lands/a6ca40ae-1637-4c24-84b8-77046687a037
https://app.nextearth.io/lands/a3cf871b-d9d1-4559-a5e1-fd6ac77fb221
https://app.nextearth.io/lands/f234e7cb-f45e-4e31-aafc-29da7cf80c09

After purchasing the painting, its owner will be able to purchase the digital land on floor price.
